下罰金\r\n；致重傷者，處3年以下有期徒刑、拘役或30萬元以下罰金。","JFULLPDF":"https://data.judicial.gov.tw/jdg/api/JDocFile/PTDM/111%2c%e4%ba%a4%e7%b0%a1%2c1152%2c20220822%2c1/pdf"},"JID":"PTDM,111,交簡,1152,20220822,1","JYEAR":"111","JCASE":"交簡","JNO":"1152","JDATE":"20220822","JTITLE":"過失傷害"}